cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for detecting corner points in event-based cameras. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics and control, which suggests cs.RO (Robotics). The use of machine learning algorithms such as Random Forests indicates cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques, which suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves the use of neural networks, which suggests cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
